io.github.kensuke1984.kibrary.dsminformation

クラス PolynomialStructure

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.kensuke1984.kibrary.dsminformation.PolynomialStructure

  • public class PolynomialStructure
extends java.lang.Object
    (input) Structure of the Earth for softwares of Direct Solution Method (DSM)
    Every depth is written in radius.
    This class is IMMUTABLE
    When you try to get values on radius of boundaries, you will get one in the shallower layer, i.e., the layer which has the radius as rmin.
    バージョン:
    0.2.1.3
    作成者:
    Kensuke Konishi

      • addBoundaries

        public PolynomialStructure addBoundaries(double... boundaries)
        半径boundariesのところに境界を作る（層を一つ増やす） Add boundaries at the radiuses. if there is already a boundary at r then nothing will be done.
        パラメータ:
        boundaries - radiuses for boundaries. Values smaller than 0 or bigger than earth radius will be ignored
        戻り値:
        a new structure which have additional layers at the input boundaries or this if there all the radiuses already exist in this
